Summary: Michal Maruska's idea: include #title in the wiki index.
Keywords: 

	* emacs-wiki.el: Merged in ideas from Michal Maruska's patch for
	including #title in the wiki index. See
        emacs-wiki-index-title-threshold for more details.
	(emacs-wiki-index-title-threshold): New variable.
	(emacs-wiki-get-title-fast): New defun.
	(emacs-wiki-file-alist-with-titles): New defun.
	(emacs-wiki-index-files-list): New convenience function.
	(emacs-wiki-index-file-title): New convenience function.
	(emacs-wiki-index-file-page): New convenience function.
	(emacs-wiki-generate-index): Observe
	emacs-wiki-index-title-threshold.
	(emacs-wiki-index): More verbose, now that it takes time to
	process.
	(emacs-wiki-publish-index): More verbose, now that it takes time
	to process.

	* planner-experimental.el (planner-generate-index): Observe
	emacs-wiki-index-title-threshold.
